# Employee Attrition Prediction System

## Business Problem
Employee attrition leads to increased recruitment and training costs. This project predicts employee turnover and identifies key contributing factors.

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- SQL
- Power BI
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn

## Project Workflow
1. Data Cleaning
2. Exploratory Data Analysis
3. SQL Business Analysis
4. Machine Learning Modeling
5. Feature Importance Analysis
6. Power BI Dashboard

## Model Performance
- Accuracy: XX%
- Algorithm: Random Forest

## Key Findings
- Overtime significantly increases attrition risk.
- Lower income employees are more likely to leave.
- Job satisfaction impacts employee retention.

## Business Recommendations
- Reduce excessive overtime.
- Improve employee engagement.
- Monitor high-risk groups proactively.